Task 1
----------------
Let us start with creating instances in AWS/Azure
Create 2 instances i.e - redhat and ubuntu.

In UBUNTU lets install mysql and postgress server
For installation follow the steps from following links
https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-mysql-on-ubuntu-20-04
https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-and-use-postgresql-on-ubuntu-20-04



Install Remote Web Servers
  For this we have to install HTTPD (Apache) in redhat and install nginix in ubuntu
